asset.title: 2011 - 2014 Dodge Challenger, 2012 - 2014 Chrysler 300 & Dodge Charger 6.4L Air Intake Installation
asset.description:
See how easy it is to add more performance to the 2011-2013 Dodge Challenger, Chrysler 300 and 2012 or 2013 Dodge Charger 6.4L.

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=63-1565

K&N 63-1565 air intake modification showed an estimated gain of 21.95 horsepower at 5216 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer. 

K&N 63-1565 fits the following: 
2014 DODGE CHARGER 6.4L V8 
2014 DODGE CHALLENGER 6.4L V8 
2014 CHRYSLER 300 6.4L V8 
2013 DODGE CHARGER 6.4L V8 
2013 DODGE CHALLENGER 6.4L V8 
2013 CHRYSLER 300 6.4L V8
2012 DODGE CHARGER 6.4L V8 
2012 DODGE CHALLENGER 6.4L V8 
2012 CHRYSLER 300 6.4L V8  
2011 DODGE CHALLENGER 6.4L V8
 
Check http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=69-2545TP for an up to date application list.
